main_body:
Belgium is hereby authorized to grant aid totalling Bfrs 6 934 900 000 to the Belgian coal industry for the 1989 calendar year. The total amount shall be made up of the following aid:
1. aid to cover operating losses not exceeding Bfrs 6 709 200 000;
2. aid to sales of coal and coke to the iron and steel industry of the Community not exceeding Bfrs 223 300 000;
3. aid for training the workforce not exceeding Bfrs 2 400 000.
